    "Second, Segura-Bedmar et al. [21] found that fine-tuning BERT models resulted in the best NER performance on the RareDis corpus.",
    "Therefore, we adopted the same approach for a consistent comparison.",
    "Figure 2 illustrates the architecture of the BERT model.",
    "To fine-tune this model on the RareDis corpus, we performed a series of pre-processing tasks.",
    "First, we split the texts into tokens with the BERT tokenizer and added special tokens (i.e., CLS and SEP) to the beginning and end of each tokenized sequence, respectively."
